<!id: type-inference>
<!description: Hints for improving type inference usage with var>
<!severity: info>
<!minJavaVersion: 10>
<!tags: modernization, readability>

// Hint-only: suggest var for local variables with obvious type from constructor
"Consider using 'var' for local variable with obvious type (Java 10+)":
new $Type($args) :: sourceVersionGE(10)
;;
